name: sfchronicle
text: Explaining why the @sfchronicle election results map has called the state of Arizona: Our results page uses data from the Associated Press. AP called Arizona, with its 11 electoral votes, for Joe Biden on Tuesday afternoon. https://t.co/4Wr6CnjTjf

text:

text:

After only 2.5 hours, jury reached verdict & I barely made it to court today. A wild finish to this tragic saga.
